Package gov.nasa.larcfm.ACCoRD

Class TCASTable

java.lang.Object
gov.nasa.larcfm.ACCoRD.TCASTable
All Implemented Interfaces:
ParameterTable, ParameterAcceptor, ParameterProvider
public class TCASTable extends Object implements ParameterTable
TCAS table with user-defined numbers of sensitivity levels. Note: this new version should be mostly compatible with the previous version from an API standpoint, with the exception of the getSensitivityLevel() methods. These had previously been static and are now instance methods. New methods allow users to define an arbitrary number of sensitivity levels, not just 8. *

    • getLevelAltitudeUpperBound
